title: "Sovereign Trace Protocol"
abstract: >
  A permanent personal significance infrastructure. Triple-time
  cryptographic stamp binding textual entries simultaneously to
  Gregorian, Hebrew lunisolar (full four dehiyot, civil-day convention),
  and 13 Moon Dreamspell calendar representations via SHA-256 hash.
  FROZEN-2.0 — written once, verified once, deployed permanently.
  Zero external dependencies. Stdlib only.
